Mart_Logic: (populate count(Loan_no_new) where, Product_NHB = 'Other Loan') - (Sr. no 13 + Sr. no 19)
SQL_Query:
SELECT count(case when TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES =0 and LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE>='2025-04-01' AND DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE)<DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',DATE{{report_dates}}) THEN loan_number_new end)-
count(case when TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES <>0 AND DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE)<DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',DATE{{report_dates}}) THEN loan_number_new end)
AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE UPPER(TRIM(PRODUCT_NHB)) IN ('OTHER LOAN')
  AND COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)),'') NOT IN ('INDIVIDUAL', 'CORPORATE')
  and coalesce(loan_amount,0)<>0
  AND REPORT_DATE = {{report_dates}};

Mart_Logic: (populate sum(HL_Bifur_of_sanction_amt) where, Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 27 + Sr.No 33)
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    SUM(CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(UPPER(Product_NHB)),'NULL') <> 'OTHER LOAN' 
        THEN HL_bifur_of_Sanction_amt 
        ELSE 0 
    END)
    -
    (COALESCE(SUM(CASE
        WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND TRIM(UPPER(Product_NHB)) IN ('PURCHASE', 'CONSTRUCTION')
            AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL
        THEN HL_bifur_of_Sanction_amt
        ELSE 0
    END), 0) +
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE
        WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND TRIM(UPPER(Product_NHB)) = 'RESALE PROPERTY PURCHASE'
        THEN HL_bifur_of_Sanction_amt
        ELSE 0
    END), 0) +
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE
        WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND TRIM(UPPER(Product_NHB)) = 'REPAIR AND RENOVATION LOAN'
        THEN HL_bifur_of_Sanction_amt
        ELSE 0
    END), 0))
    AS housing_loans_to_others
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}});

Mart_Logic: (populate sum(NHL_bifur_of_Sanction_amt)   where, Product_NHB = 'Other Loan') - (Sr. no 38 + Sr. no 44)

WHERE UPPER(TRIM(PRODUCT_NHB)) IN ('OTHER LOAN')

Mart_Logic: (populate count(Loan_no_new) where, Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 102 + Sr.No 108)
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    (

        SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new) 
        FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
        WHERE Product_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN'
        AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
    ) 
    - 
    (
        (

            SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new) 
            FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
            WHERE Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL
            AND PRODUCT_NHB IN ('Purchase', 'Construction')
            AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
        )
        +
        (

            SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new) 
            FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
            WHERE Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND PRODUCT_NHB = 'Resale Property Purchase'
            AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
        )
        +
        (

            SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new) 
            FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
            WHERE Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
            AND PRODUCT_NHB = 'Repair and Renovation Loan'
            AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
        )
    )
    -
    (

        SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new) 
        FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
        WHERE Product_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN'
        AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL
        AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
    ) AS Housing_Loans_to_Others;

(populate countof distinct(Loan_no_new) where, Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 252 + Sr.No 258)
(populate count of distinct(Loan_no_new) where, Product_NHB = 'Other Loan') - (Sr. no 263 + Sr. no 269)
SQL_Query:

Mart_Logic: (populate sum(HL_Bifur_of_disb_amt) where, Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 277 + Sr.No 283)
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    COALESCE(
        SUM(CASE WHEN Product_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN'  THEN HL_bifur_of_disb_amt ELSE 0 END)
        -
        SUM(CASE WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL' 
                  AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL 
                  AND Product_NHB IN ('Purchase', 'Construction') 
                  THEN HL_bifur_of_disb_amt ELSE 0 END) 
        -
        SUM(CASE WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL' 
                  AND Product_NHB = 'Resale Property Purchase' 
                  THEN HL_bifur_of_disb_amt ELSE 0 END) 
        -
        SUM(CASE WHEN Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL' 
                  AND Product_NHB = 'Repair and Renovation Loan' 
                  THEN HL_bifur_of_disb_amt ELSE 0 END)
        -
        SUM(CASE WHEN Product_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN' 
                  AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL 
                  THEN HL_bifur_of_disb_amt ELSE 0 END) 
    , 0) AS Housing_Loans_to_Others
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.DISBURSEMENT_PERIOD_MART
WHERE Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}});

Mart_Logic: (populate count(Loan_no_new) where, nhb_Product <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 302 + Sr.No 308)
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN' 
        THEN LOAN_NUMBER_NEW 
    END) -
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)), '') = 'INDIVIDUAL'
             AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL
             AND UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)) IN ('PURCHASE', 'CONSTRUCTION', 'RESALE PROPERTY PURCHASE', 'REPAIR AND RENOVATION LOAN')
        THEN LOAN_NUMBER_NEW 
    END) -
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
             AND (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL 
                  OR (UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE' AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL))
        THEN LOAN_NUMBER_NEW 
    END) AS final_output
FROM 
    DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE 
    REPORT_DATE = LAST_DAY(DATEADD(MONTH,-1,{{report_dates}}))
    AND IND_AS_EAD > 0.9;

SQL_Query:
SELECT 
	ROUND(COALESCE(SUM(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN' 
        THEN HL_bifurcation_of__EAD 
    END),0) -
    COALESCE(SUM(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)), '') = 'INDIVIDUAL'
             AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL
             AND UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)) IN ('PURCHASE', 'CONSTRUCTION', 'RESALE PROPERTY PURCHASE', 'REPAIR AND RENOVATION LOAN')
        THEN HL_bifurcation_of__EAD 
    END),0) -
    COALESCE(SUM(DISTINCT CASE 
        WHEN COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
             AND (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL 
                  OR (UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE' AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL))
        THEN HL_bifurcation_of__EAD 
    END),0),2) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM 
    DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE 
    REPORT_DATE = {{report_dates}}
    AND IND_AS_EAD > 0.9
    AND TRIM(Asset_classification_Ind_AS) = 'Stage 3';

Mart_Logic: (populate count(NHL_bifur_of__EAD) where, nhb_Product = 'Other Loan' and staging = 'Stage 3' ) - (Sr. no 498 + Sr. no 504)
(populate count(Loan_no_new) where, Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan') - (Sr. No 2 + Sr.No 8)
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
(
SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new)
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE PRODUCT_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN'
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
) - (
SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new)
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
AND (
(CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL AND PRODUCT_NHB IN ('Purchase', 'Construction'))
OR (PRODUCT_NHB = 'Resale Property Purchase')
OR (PRODUCT_NHB = 'Repair and Renovation Loan')
)
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
) - (
SELECT COUNT(Loan_number_new)
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL
AND PRODUCT_NHB <> 'OTHER LOAN'
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
AND Report_Date IN ({{report_dates}})
) AS housing_loans_to_others;

Mart_Logic:
populate count(Loan_no_new) where,
1- Product_NHB <> 'Other Loan'
2- CRE_RH_Tagging is not NULL
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(CASE 
        WHEN (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL OR 
              (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE'))
         AND TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES = 0 
         AND LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE >= '2025-04-01'
		 AND DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE)<DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',DATE{{report_dates}})
        THEN 1 
    END) - 
    COUNT(CASE 
        WHEN (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL OR 
              (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE'))
         AND TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES <> 0
		 AND DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE)<DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',DATE{{report_dates}})
        THEN 1 
    END) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(PRODUCT_NHB)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
  AND COALESCE(loan_amount,0) <> 0
  AND REPORT_DATE = {{report_dates}};

AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1

AND COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)),'') = 'CORPORATE'
and coalesce(loan_amount,0)<>0
AND DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE)=DATE_TRUNC('MONTH',DATE{{report_dates}})
AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};

populate count(Loan_no_new) where,

2- CRE_RH_Tagging is not NULL
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(CASE 
        WHEN (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL OR 
              (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE'))
         AND TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES = 0 
         AND LOAN_AUTHOR_DATE >= '2025-04-01'
        THEN 1 
    END) - 
    COUNT(CASE 
        WHEN (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL OR 
              (CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE'))
         AND TAGGING_OF_CANCELLED_CASES <> 0
        THEN 1 
    END) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.SANCTION_PERIOD_MART_V1
WHERE COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(PRODUCT_NHB)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
  AND COALESCE(loan_amount,0) <> 0
  AND REPORT_DATE = {{report_dates}};

WHERE IND_AS_EAD>0.9
AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'INDIVIDUAL'
AND CRE_RH_Tagging is null
AND UPPER(TRIM(ROI_Type)) = 'FLOATING'
AND ROI_as_on_reporting_date > 20 and ROI_as_on_reporting_date <=30
AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};

Mart_Logic:
Select count(Loan_number_new) where
1- Customer_type = 'CORPORATE'
2- nhb_Product <> 'Other Loan'
3- ROI_Type = 'Fixed'
4- ROI_as_on_reporting_date <= 10%
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(CASE 
            WHEN CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL THEN LOAN_NUMBER_NEW 
            WHEN UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE' AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL THEN LOAN_NUMBER_NEW 
          END) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM 
    DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE 
    COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
    AND IND_AS_EAD > 0.9
	AND UPPER(TRIM(ROI_Type)) = 'FIXED'
	AND ROI_as_on_reporting_date <=10
	AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};

    WHEN UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'INDIVIDUAL' AND CRE_RH_TAGGING IS  NOT NULL THEN NHL_bifurcation_of__EAD
    END)/10000000,0),2)  AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE IND_AS_EAD>0.9
AND UPPER(TRIM(ROI_Type)) = 'FIXED'
AND ROI_as_on_reporting_date > 20 and ROI_as_on_reporting_date <=30
AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};

Mart_Logic:
Select sum(HL_POS) where
1- Customer_type = 'INDIVIDUAL'
2- nhb_Product <> 'Other Loan'
3- ROI_Type = 'Floating'
4- ROI_as_on_reporting_date > 30%
SQL_Query:
SELECT ROUND(COALESCE(sum(HL_bifurcation_of__EAD)/10000000,0),2) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
 FROM DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE IND_AS_EAD>0.9
AND UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'INDIVIDUAL'
AND CRE_RH_Tagging is null
AND COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)),'') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
AND UPPER(TRIM(ROI_Type)) = 'FLOATING'
AND ROI_as_on_reporting_date >30
AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};

3- ROI_Type = 'Floating'

SQL_Query:

Mart_Logic:
Select sum(HL_POS) where
1- Customer_type = 'CORPORATE'
2- nhb_Product = 'Other Loan'
3- ROI_Type = 'Floating'
4- ROI_as_on_reporting_date > 30%
SQL_Query:
SELECT 
    ROUND(COALESCE(SUM(CASE 
            WHEN CRE_RH_Tagging IS NOT NULL THEN HL_bifurcation_of__EAD 
            WHEN UPPER(TRIM(Customer_type)) = 'CORPORATE' AND CRE_RH_Tagging IS NULL THEN HL_bifurcation_of__EAD 
          END)/10000000,0),2) AS FINAL_OUTPUT
FROM 
    DISHA_MART_ANALYTICS.REGULATORY_MART.OUTSTANDING_MART
WHERE 
    COALESCE(UPPER(TRIM(NHB_PRODUCT)), '') <> 'OTHER LOAN'
    AND IND_AS_EAD > 0.9
	AND UPPER(TRIM(ROI_Type)) = 'FLOATING'
	AND ROI_as_on_reporting_date >= 30 
	AND REPORT_DATE ={{report_dates}};
